        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2599245123" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10450426971325700074">Lowdown by author Anthony Schneider is a gritty look into the lives of a mob family and forbidden love. It&apos;s running from the feds and loving someone locked up in the federal penitentiary. I absolutely loved this book as well as characters in it! I greatly recommend this novel!!<br/>Thank you Netgalley and the publisher for a copy of Lowdown in exchange for an honest review.</span>
  <span id="freeText10450426971325700074" style="display:none">Lowdown by author Anthony Schneider is a gritty look into the lives of a mob family and forbidden love. It's running from the feds and loving someone locked up in the federal penitentiary. I absolutely loved this book as well as characters in it! I greatly recommend this novel!!<br />Thank you Netgalley and the publisher for a copy of Lowdown in exchange for an honest review.</span>
