    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2601790767" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4659283039730712917">First let me say that I love anything about the mob. Casino, Goodfellas and The Godfather saga are my favorite movies. This book really tells of the life of organized crime and all it entails. It was part crime thriller part romance and the combination of the 2 is what kept me reading. At times I wasn’t going to finish this book because of all the characters to keep track of and I really thought it was way too long, but in the end it turned out to be a pretty good book. The ending was wonderful </span>
  <span id="freeText4659283039730712917" style="display:none">First let me say that I love anything about the mob. Casino, Goodfellas and The Godfather saga are my favorite movies. This book really tells of the life of organized crime and all it entails. It was part crime thriller part romance and the combination of the 2 is what kept me reading. At times I wasn’t going to finish this book because of all the characters to keep track of and I really thought it was way too long, but in the end it turned out to be a pretty good book. The ending was wonderful and heartfelt. Thank you netgalley for letting me give an honest review of this book.</span>
