<span id="freeTextContainer6001231574395364311">Anthony Schneider has been published in McSweeneys, Conjunctions, Bold Type, Details, US News &amp; World Report, as well as fiction anthologies and other magazines. A graduate of the University of Pennsylvania and the NYU Creative Writing Program, he was awarded a MacDowell Fellowship and was a Pushcart Prize finalist. <br/><br/>His second novel, LOWDOWN, is published by Permanent Press. <br/><br/>His first novel, REPER</span>
  <span id="freeText6001231574395364311" style="display:none">Anthony Schneider has been published in McSweeneys, Conjunctions, Bold Type, Details, US News &amp; World Report, as well as fiction anthologies and other magazines. A graduate of the University of Pennsylvania and the NYU Creative Writing Program, he was awarded a MacDowell Fellowship and was a Pushcart Prize finalist. <br /><br />His second novel, LOWDOWN, is published by Permanent Press. <br /><br />His first novel, REPERCUSSIONS, won an Indies Book of the Year Award. <br /><br />He divides his time between New York and London. <br /><br /></span>
